{"tid":601912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳內地生或踴躍報考　考評局：兩岸逾240高校下學年招收DSE考生","createTime":"2018-03-22T15:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T15:32:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4b12354885acabef12f8477a4e69f11b25331588","tid":601912,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180322/s00001/0b752e35b5d77a3ef62947a2715d9b62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180322%2Fs00001%2F0b752e35b5d77a3ef62947a2715d9b62.jpg&h=50b8f543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地高考競爭激烈，部分人轉投眼光於香港香港中學文憑試（DSE），近日又有本地傳媒報道有本地補習社，開設專門針對內地生的DSE補習班，惹來部分本港家長和學生關注。考評局今日在其官方網誌發文，稱本年度非本地的考生，僅佔DSE整體考生的一小部分。<br />\n<br />\n網誌題為〈面向本港 國際認可的文憑試〉。文章引用2018年DSE考生數字，指以香港身份證以外的身份證明，來報考的學生及自修生，在整體59,000多名考生中，僅佔0.3%。考評局呼籲同學可專心準備應考，不要被「大量內地生應考DSE」之說所困擾。<br />\n<br />\n文章另有內容提及，任何符合報考DSE資格的人士，均可用自修生名義來報考，並沒有國籍等其他限制或資格。考評局不會收集與處理考務安排無關的個人資料，故沒有內地學生報考文憑試的統計數字。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，現時認可DSE的海外高等院校，已由2012年約100間，增至目前超過270間。2018/19學年，有102所內地高等院校，會免試招收本港的文憑試考生；香港學生亦可直接以文憑試成績，報讀台灣約140所大學。<br />\n<br />\n另外，教育局回應查詢時，則強調教資會資助的各間大學，每年提供15,000個第一年學士學位課程學額予本地生，並都只能以超額收生形式，錄取非本地學生入讀教資會資助課程，合共人數不得超過教資會上述學額的兩成，所以非本地學生不會與本地學生競爭資助學額。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180322/s00001/1521726333159\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180322%2Fs00001%2F1521726333159&d=9r6hOT1uquhmcijAzKx0j%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c91cd2ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180322%2Fs00001%2F1521726333159&h=3e2f9eed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180322/s00001/1521726333159</a>"},{"pid":"a7a71503a7a17ca9ed984eaca253c4162637938f","tid":601912,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:17:31.000Z","msg":"支那人可以報 jupas 咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005aa812fc3749146793d8084e42c57618c909a1","tid":601912,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6616bb332616a348757025dcf9f9194694d832ea","tid":601912,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:24:36.000Z","msg":"不嬲都好多支那人去考會考<br />\n入到U仲多支那人做你同學"},{"pid":"6b824cf6e90f0c061d41358787ee544be15f7920","tid":601912,"uid":176166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:27:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2abcfad14d70785de58be9eea00ef7539a82b01d","tid":601912,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"你話唔係溝淡真係冇人信"},{"pid":"c78a109f9c8d6694940a726a8155e6c54bfea3d7","tid":601912,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:31:44.000Z","msg":"內地?<br />\n<br />\n咁邊度係外地呀？<br />\n<br />\n依家並唔係要捉你錯別字， 而係捉你講匪語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係中国或支那或鬼國"},{"pid":"eea44bc17fa71d52cb0a37d66ce84bec27d78f4a","tid":601912,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7a71503a7a17ca9ed984eaca253c4162637938f","tid":601912,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:17:31.000Z","msg":"支那人可以報 jupas 咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:32:13.000Z","msg":"好似冇規定香港人先可以報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}